@node Description "5D-JoinConf Description"
5D-JoinConf has been coded by SvEN tHE CREAToR/5D!

It is a replacement for the normal 'J'-Command of AmiExpress v3.x+.
You can also use cursor keys!
@endnode
@node Installation "5D-JoinConf Installation"
Copy all files which are in the archive bbs directory
to your bbs directory.

Contents of archive:
===================

BBS/
    Commands/
        BBSCmd/
            J.info
    Doors/
        5D-JoinConf/
            5D-JoinConf
            5D-JoinConf.info
            5D-JoinConf.Guide

===================

@endnode
