@node Special "5D-JoinConf Special things"
If you want to show an ansi above the normal JoinConf-Screen then simply
save it under 'Doors:5D-JoinConf/5D-JoinConf.txt'. If you want to use
the mode where the conferences are shown one under another then simply
add the tooltype 'OLD_MODE' to your 'CONFCONFIG.info'. Sure, the password
option is back again and for using it you only need to add the tooltype
'PASSWORD.<CONF_NUMBER>=<PASSWORD', for example: 'PASSWORD.2=DOSE' to the
icon talken about above. I hope that it is like you want it to be but if
there are any things which should be changed then call me at my board.
@endnode
